description:
On this week’s episode of #ANNProfiles with Alyssa Truman, Ronny Nalin shares his experience growing up in a small church community which became his extended family. 

Listen to the full episode to learn how his family stayed connected with God at home while being part of a larger family in a region where he built lasting relationships with Adventist youth from all over Italy. #Italy #AdventistYouth

Watch the full episode by copying this link into your browser: 
https://youtu.be/80SvJgkMBTo
fulltitle: The Church as Family: Making the Difference
